Change Point Report

Dataset: Application_2.csv

  • The processed data contains annual max streamflow measurements between 1928 and 2018.
  • There are 91 values in the dataset, 0 of which are missing.

Exploratory Data Analysis

Mann-Whitney-Pettitt Test

Purpose: Detect abrupt changes in the annual max streamflow data.

Result: There is a statistically significant change point in 1972.

Mann-Kendall-Sneyers Test

Purpose: Detect the beginning of a change in trend in the annual max streamflow data.

Result: There are 2 statistically significant trend changes.
